   Business Brief -- Procter &amp; Gamble Co.:
   Bar Soap Plant Expansion
   To Create Up to 50 Jobs
</HL>
<DATE>
08/03/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   PG
</CO>
<LP>
   Procter &amp; Gamble Co. said it will expand and modernize its
Ivorydale bar soap plant in St. Bernard, Ohio.
   The project includes a 65,000-square-foot addition to the
existing bar soap plant. About 45 to 50 new jobs will be
added to the soap plant, which already employs about 750
people.
